PROJECT HIGH SUN — REPOSITORY BOUNDARY

Everything for Nahar Meridian and Daybreak OS Meridian belongs under /meridian.
The repository root remains the Nahar Pico / Project Small Sun application.
Meridian code must not import, overwrite, rename, or depend on Pico source files.
Shared lore and simulated Pico-link features may exist, but their implementation remains inside /meridian.
